<br>
Now the reason for looking into one of these things is that I allmost always fail to channel my regular gate spell (or right click items, such as my Bio Orb), and I always get interrupted.<br>
<br>
From memory, my Channeling skill is 220 (level 55), which sounds high enough to effectively work in my mind!  What other factors, if any, will help me channel my spells when I'm getting hit?  Do I need more AC, better AGI?  Does the amount of damage you take affect your ability to channel?<br>
<br>
Cheers<br>
<br>
 <p>Canelin.<br>
Magician of the 55th something or other.</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zaniel>Zaniel</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 141<br> <font color=#333333>(1/22/03 12:28:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=515.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Channeling - why does it never work for me?</span><hr size=1> Its not the amount of damage per se its the distance you are pushed and heavier more frequent hits push you further. This is why you can channel more easily when wedged in a corner and why guilds &quot;push&quot; gating mobs.<br>
<br>
Your ability to overcoming this is measured by only two basic factors, your channelling skill and to some degree modified by your DEX. This is why hybrids with primal / Focus are so good at channelling, their DEX is sky high (and short cast time spells but that's another story). If you are prepared to lose AC/MR try and get a focus cast on you if you are having problems. <p>Zaniel Stormseeker<br>
65th Arch Convoker</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=canelin@themagicianstower>Canelin</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 104<br> <font color=#333333>(1/22/03 1:34:28 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm30.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=515.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Channeling - why does it never work for me?</span><hr size=1> Thanks - I've got no idea what my DEX is.  It's not really a skill I've ever been worried about.<br>
